title: Kylie Jenner Works On Her Fitness In Tiny Sports Bra And Leggings
text:
Kylie Jenner Works On Her Fitness In Tiny Sports Bra And Leggings Sporty is the new casual. Carly Ledbetter Associate Entertainment Editor, The Huffington Post Posted: 10/12/2015 03:15 PM EDT 
Kylie Jenner isn't shy when it comes to showing skin. The 18-year-old reality star proved that fact Sunday when she shared an Instagram photo with her 38 million followers, clad in just a sports bra and leggings. 
The photo got Jenner an easy million likes in just under 24 hours: A photo posted by King Kylie (@kyliejenner) on Oct 11, 2015 at 12:59pm PDT 
Jenner has developed a penchant for wearing sports bras and leggings as complete outfits, and it appears to be one of her favorite looks.
